dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon shapefile is an index to 1:200,000 scale maps of Mongolia, Manchuria (China), Siberia (Russia), titled '二十万分一地誌圖 - Nijūmanbun no ichi Chishizu.’ To create this index, footprints were generated using the fishnet tool, and metadata were supplied for the digitized paper maps by Stanford University Libraries. After the footprints were created, the shapefile was trimmed and labeled according to the sources.
